.git.backup.*
# Ignore workflow files by glob (not by directory) so individual files
# can be surgically un-ignored below. A bare `.github/workflows/`
# excludes the directory itself, and gitignore cannot re-include a
# file under an excluded parent directory.
.github/workflows/*
# Surgical un-ignore for the schema-drift CI guard added in Task #814.
# The rest of the workflow tree was ignored after the workflow scope
# was removed historically (see commit 767c71171 "Remove workflows
# directory"). This file must be tracked so GitHub Actions actually
# runs the schema-drift check on every PR — without it, the guard from
# Task #814 would only exist on the local Replit environment.
!.github/workflows/schema-drift-check.yml
